&lt;b&gt;About&lt;/b&gt;

Based in British Columbia, Canada, LunaNode Hosting Inc. first launched in August 2013, focusing on low-cost, reliable KVM virtual private server hosting. We use OpenStack for our back-end and an in-house billing / VM management panel called lndynamic on the front-end. We are committed to security and &lt;a href="https://www.lunanode.com/privacy"&gt;privacy&lt;/a&gt; and believe in the necessity of free software (&lt;a href="https://github.com/LunaNode/"&gt;see our GitHub profile&lt;/a&gt;). Our staff consists of experienced developers, system administrators, and network engineers; we are constantly monitoring and improving our infrastructure to ensure maximal uptime, and developing new tools to help you better manage your virtual machines.

